Tga '''Zagura''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵣⴰⴳⵓⵔⴰ''') nɣ '''Tazagurt''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⴰⵣⴰⴳⵓⵔⵜ''') yat tmdint imẓẓyn illan ɣ tuẓẓumt-agmuḍan n tgldit n [[Lmɣrib]], twala i tsga n [[Tasga n Dṛɛa-Tafilalt|Dṛɛa-Tafilalt]].

== Aẓur n yism ==
Ikka-d yism n Zagura tutlayt [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]]. Illa maytinin izd tucka zɣ ism n wasif n Zagur, yili maytinin zɣ taqbilt n Zwagr.

== Imzdaɣ ==
Ar ittini usidn lli ittuyskar ɣ usggwas n 2004 mas tiɣrmt ad zdɣn gis uggar n 40 067 n middn. Imzdaɣn n tiɣrmt ad gan [[imaziɣn]] yilin gis waɛrabn ula nttni, ar sawaln 12.7% n imzdaɣ n tiɣrmt ad s tutlayt [[Tutlayt Taclḥit|tacḥit]] d 13.5% s [[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|tamaziɣt n waṭlas anammas]].

== Asnmkta ==
Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2014 mas<ref>[http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/ RGPH 2014 - Site HCP]</ref>:

=== Aslmd ===

* Asɣl n taqubbanit (middn lli ur ssin ad aqran wala ad ttaran) : 25,8%
* Asɣl n imzdaɣ lli iɣran ar usinan n usmdi nɣd uggar : 19%

=== Tadamsa ===

* Asɣl n imzdaɣ lli llan ɣ isggasn nnsn n twuri : 40,5%
* Asɣl n tarwuri (middn lli ur ṭṭafn tawuri) : 18,9%
* Asɣl n imzdaɣ lli swurin dar lmxzn (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 25,1%
* Asɣl n imzdaɣ lli swurin ɣ uslig (nɣ kantin swurin gis) : 37,9%

